    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight as interesting as you can, hack your enemies, use tricks to get more subscribers and earn the big credits. You need those to upgrade your ship and travel to further planets. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the market city, meet new Artificials and find a way to fix your dying friend.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246590/extras/2cc5cf64212352098e45b4bd044a2afe.poster.avif?t=1760690289\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246590/extras/2cc5cf64212352098e45b4bd044a2afe.webm?t=1760690289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246590/extras/2cc5cf64212352098e45b4bd044a2afe.mp4?t=1760690289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Powerful weapons, fun and innovative hacking mechanics, </strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Clean next gen graphics </strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Adrenaline-pumping dark techno music</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Intriguing story, quests and exploration</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet a variety of Artificials (maybe even find humans) on your journey to save a friend from certain death. Explore planetary systems, and discover the sad truth about humans and what led to their downfall.</p>",
